commit.message: Attemp to move back to subprocess

Added text wrap logic

- The text will wrap at a full line instead of cutting in the middle of
a word.  Initial test, might not work

Added testing features

- Allows printing to be disabled to test

Printer control via command line arguments

- Added a library in python2 which allows the printer to be used fully with command line arguments, which can be called from python3 to work as a wrapper effectively
